original_title: Not the End of the World
overview: James and Tracey couldn't wait for the end of the world. The problem is, it happened without them. All of their friends have advanced to the new dimension prophesied by their leader, Mr. Splain. But they are left behind. Now they must try and make sense of it all and figure out how to carry on. Will they try to reassemble their old lives or attempt to forge a new way?
title: Not the End of the World
